    "en": {
      "title": "Gorbachev is on his way",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The funeral of Mikhail Gorbachev, who is considered the last Soviet leader, was held in the capital Moscow amid military honors.",
        "It is reported that Russian President Vladimir Putin did not attend the funeral due to his busy schedule. Mikhail Gorbachev was 91 years old when he passed away after a long illness."
